dc_description_s: This line data layer represents trails for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Brown_Trails_2017.gdb'.
uw_supplemental_s: For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://browncounty.maps.arcgis.com/apps/webappviewer/index.html?id=61fba3fd419045e48aa6ba759838387cThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
